## üñ•Ô∏è Windows

### Installation (Windows)
1. **Download the executable**  
   - Go to üëâ [yt-dlp Releases](https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp/releases/latest)  
   - Download `yt-dlp.exe`

2. **Place the file**  
   - Put `yt-dlp.exe` in a folder, e.g., `C:\yt-dlp`

3. **Add to PATH (optional but recommended)**  
   - Search "Environment Variables" in Windows.  
   - Edit `Path` ‚Üí Add `C:\yt-dlp`.  
   - Now you can run `yt-dlp` from any directory.

4. **Alternative: Install with pip**
   ```bash
   pip install -U yt-dlp


###Usage (Windows)###

Open Command Prompt (cmd) or PowerShell

Run commands like: yt-dlp https://youtube.com/watch?v=abcd1234


###üçè macOS###
Installation (macOS)

Using Homebrew (Recommended)

Run commands like:  brew install yt-dlp

Using pip

Run commands like: pip3 install -U yt-dlp

Manual binary installation

Run commands like:  sudo curl -L https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp/releases/latest/download/yt-dlp \
-o /usr/local/bin/yt-dlp
sudo chmod a+rx /usr/local/bin/yt-dlp


Usage (macOS)

Open Terminal

Run:yt-dlp "https://youtube.com/watch?v=abcd1234"



###üêß Linux###
Installation (Linux)

Using pip

Run commands like: pip install -U yt-dlp


Download binary

Run commands like:sudo wget https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp/releases/latest/download/yt-dlp -O /usr/local/bin/yt-dlp
sudo chmod a+rx /usr/local/bin/yt-dlp

Arch Linux (AUR)

Run commands like: yay -S yt-dlp

Usage (Linux)

Open Terminal

Run:yt-dlp https://youtube.com/watch?v=abcd1234


###‚ö° Common Commands###
```
Download video
Run:yt-dlp <video_url>

Download audio only (mp3)
Run:yt-dlp -x --audio-format mp3 <video_url>

Custom output filename
Run:yt-dlp -o "%(title)s.%(ext)s" <video_url>

Download playlist
Run:yt-dlp <playlist_url>

Download specific items from playlist
Run:yt-dlp <playlist_url> --playlist-items 1,3,5

Download with subtitles
Run:yt-dlp --write-subs --sub-lang en <url>

Limit download speed
Run:yt-dlp --limit-rate 500K <url>

Resume interrupted download
Run:yt-dlp -c <url>
```
